"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-olympic-duo-nasty-fall-out-best-player-world-branded-insincere-21337707\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympic tennis starsIga Swiatekand Danielle Collins had a nasty fall-out on Wednesday, with the Polish world No.1 branded 'insincere' by her opponent.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 51, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Collins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Danielle Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Collins\"}, {\"begin\": 96, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.6185738736529771, \"rank\": 0.45837156162438125, \"text\": \"Polish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swiatek is the best current female tennis player in the world and is dominant across the WTA Tour, especially on clay, having won theFrench Openfor three straight years.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old has an incredible tally of 11,005 ranking points at the moment - 2832 more than the world No.2 Coco Gauff - showing just how strong she is.\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swiatek has been caught up in controversy, though, after Team USA star Collins slammed her following their tense quarter-final showdown at Roland-Garros.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.995798366773546, \"rank\": 0.0030585956795475635, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9854134555037384, \"rank\": 0.014802460528940051, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the match, Collins told Swiatek to 'play at the server's pace' after the Polish star held up her hand to halt the American's service motion.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9854134555037384, \"rank\": 0.014802460528940051, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}, {\"begin\": 715, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.6185738736529771, \"rank\": 0.45837156162438125, \"text\": \"Polish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}, {\"begin\": 756, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999954918791728, \"rank\": 3.634773503782419e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Collins later appeared to hit Swiatek with the ball - and the world No.1 was also jeered onto the court for taking a long break at the end of the second set.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 784, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9854134555037384, \"rank\": 0.014802460528940051, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American eventually retired to hand Swiatek victory - and following a heated exchange on the court - Collins ripped into the top-seed in her press conference.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 947, \"end\": 955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999954918791728, \"rank\": 3.634773503782419e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9854134555037384, \"rank\": 0.014802460528940051, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I told Iga she did not have to be insincere about, you know, my injury,' Collins said.\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.107922302675553e-14, \"text\": \"Iga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\"}, {\"begin\": 1181, \"end\": 1188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9854134555037384, \"rank\": 0.014802460528940051, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is a lot that happens on camera, and there are a lot of people with a ton of charisma and come out and are one way on camera and another way in the locker room.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'And I just have not had the best experience, and I do not really feel like anybody needs to be insincere.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They can be the way that they are.\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can accept that, and I do not need the fakeness.'\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"pic.twitter.com/vR5Bk80IN5  Swiatek has issued a response and has insisted that she has no idea where Collins is coming from.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.9854134555037384, \"rank\": 0.014802460528940051, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I will not argue about it, because I have never done anything unpleasant towards her,' Swiatek said.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just wanted to congratulate her on her successful career, because we all know that this is her last year on tour.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Honestly, I do not know what she meant because we did not even have any interactions that could have caused her to say that to me.\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Generally speaking, during tournaments, when we go out and have time to change our clothes, we are entitled to five minutes.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here I asked the lady who escorted me how much time I had.\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not tell me that.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'She replied that they do not count time here and that I should just leave when I feel like it.\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I used this time to change and cool down, and then I returned to the court.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I honestly did not know how much time had passed, but I did not do anything against the rules, so I do not really know what the whole situation was about.'\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic triathlete makes disgusting revelation after swimming in polluted Paris river  ArrowMORE:Olympic gold medallist awkwardly squirms in confrontation over Strictly 2024 'leak'  ArrowMORE:Michael Phelps reacts to Leon Marchand's historic Olympic double gold in Paris  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2984703275162154e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2790, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1588482969089635e-23, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedi